    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Note that pre-0.5.0, `call` performed its own encoding (\"pad to 32 bytes and concatenate\") which was different from ABI encoding. We removed this special case for 0.5.0 and now `call` just takes a `bytes` and passes it on as is without modification.",
